title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The truth is the unusual takes some getting used to and it might require a little extra time to get your bearings today. Perhaps you are hoping to make a good first impression when starting a new job, visiting an unfamiliar place, or meeting strangers. Whatever the specifics, the reality of a new experience rarely mirrors the fantasy of expectations to a tee. An attitude that is as free as possible of preconceptions can be your best friend, helping you make sense of the unknown and hang onto your sense of humor in the process. Have patience until you are surefooted and give yourself room to grow. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
